
UpdatE Failure :
reformart :
IT updates the batch statistics table when a batch fails during processing.
It marks the batch status as ‘FAILED’ and logs audit details like update time, date, and system ID.
The update is based on BATCH_ID and PROCESS_DATE to ensure accuracy.
Any records that fail to update are sent to an error file for manual review

update table :
This query updates the batch statistics table for failed batch runs.
It marks the batch as 'FAILED' and records who updated it, when, and at what time.
The update targets only the record matching the given BATCH_ID and PROCESS_DATE
